title: Should not re-request failing things too much. If it's a problem with expired oauth, don't re-request more than twice (and wait like 5 min between).
updated_at: "2026-07-15T05:09:44Z"
---

Should not re-request failing things too much. If it's a problem with expired oauth, don't re-request more than twice (and wait like 5 min between).

Also, once methods have failed, do not refresh them automatically unless eg the oauth token or api key is updated. Manual refreshes okay (for eg billing issues that get fixed).